## Additional Terms for Commercial Use

While this project is open source under the MIT License, if you plan to use 
this code for commercial restaurant websites, we kindly request that you:

1. **Attribution**: Include a credit/mention to the original Savora project
2. **Customization**: Modify the design significantly to make it unique to your brand
3. **Images**: Replace all stock images with your own professional photography
4. **Content**: Update all text content to reflect your restaurant's story and offerings

## Third-Party Assets

This project uses images from Unsplash.com which are provided under the 
Unsplash License (https://unsplash.com/license). Please ensure compliance 
with their terms when using or redistributing these images.

